{"tid":1432991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛孟靜表明民主派不會就施政報告見特首","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T11:27:50.000Z","uid":212626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9b9b0135a8e09b6f8b051a47a2d132c3fa6aede1","tid":1432991,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:17:44.000Z","msg":"民主派會議召集人毛孟靜表示，民主派較早前已經一致決定，不會就《施政報告》會見行政長官林鄭月娥，目前她與其他民主派亦未收到特首的會面邀請。<br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜認為，林鄭月娥最近約見不同界別的人士之中，有關人士均傾向同一立場，正正反映她的施政問題。<br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜說，民主派在6.12金鐘衝突及7.21元朗白衣人襲擊事件後，曾經要求過與林鄭月娥會面，但對方一直無回應。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473492-20190808.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473492-20190808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=ef5d8423\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473492-20190808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=697bbf77\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473492-20190808.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"e8c61483b89989aad725508b6dccbfaa8ff62ab8","tid":1432991,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"條柒婆都龜縮唔見你啦"},{"pid":"7fa770048488a619979dcd7660badc7ff959b85a","tid":1432991,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8c61483b89989aad725508b6dccbfaa8ff62ab8","tid":1432991,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:19:50.000Z","msg":"條柒婆都龜縮唔見你啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:27:50.000Z","msg":"據了解特首下周與政黨見面 就施政報告諮詢意見<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1473486-20190808.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1473486-20190808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2BzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=